{"tid":1588901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新華社批侮辱國旗褻瀆全體中國人民","createTime":"2019-09-23T04:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T11:17:29.000Z","uid":41404,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"9759ea754518964064cc0f4414989881841aa957","tid":1588901,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:41:27.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】內地傳媒批評，有人多次侮辱國旗，是對全體中國人民的褻瀆，呼籲在大是大非面前要作出正確選擇，旗幟鮮明地守護國旗。<br />\n<br />\n新華社發表評論文章，指周日在沙田大會堂有國旗被扯下並遭多人踐踏，亦有人用黑色噴漆塗污國旗，更將國旗扔進垃圾桶裡和附近的城門河中，批評這些行為是喪失良知，背德違法的惡行，凸顯暴徒對國旗與國家的仇恨。<br />\n<br />\n又指3個多月來的修例風波中，侮辱國旗的惡行不斷上演，有國旗被焚燒和扔進大海，做法是對國家和民族的侮辱，更是對全體中國人民的褻瀆。侮辱國旗者除了激起全體中國人民的強烈憤慨，亦違反《國旗法》，必將受到法律嚴懲。"},{"pid":"d29979f22ce0f702cb57a45efb75c61d93f05aa0","tid":1588901,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"a6f813e89641c917004a4784de74f7922a66a0d5","tid":1588901,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:42:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"198c0b7e6ac5c768a9aec7d13cb4278727694333","tid":1588901,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e21bbbe12fa03193be9e53ff3b16a63a9119fdd","tid":1588901,"uid":51057,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:43:57.000Z","msg":"<span st