mg src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20ab7810992918830a84bfe991c962116848230","tid":1588901,"uid":165683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:47:39.000Z","msg":"唔係香港燒 可以全球齊齊燒"},{"pid":"b5f9b8c7b637580105da42e157916f6eac0351c2","tid":1588901,"uid":180124,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:47:55.000Z","msg":"褻瀆<br />\n佢地啲蝗當自己係神？"},{"pid":"f2774bbd411b286f1aa043a1d38398c69e253f7f","tid":1588901,"uid":2429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:49:20.000Z","msg":"革命要贏只有四個字：逢中必反。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n毛澤東語錄：<br />\n<br />\n「我認為，對我們來說，一個人，一個黨，一個軍隊，或者一個學校，如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是同敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界線了。如若敵人起勁地反對我們，把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了，那就證明我們不但同敵人劃清了界線，而且證明我們的工作是很有成績的了。」<br />\n〈被敵人反對是好事而不是壞事〉，1939年5月26日<br />\n<br />\n「凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護；凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。」<br />\n〈和中央社、掃蕩報、新民報三記者的談話〉，1939年9月16日"},{"pid":"04eda93c3559bc46195d5a973b3981c0d71a23d0","tid":1588901,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4452ee10f0f209133df3badfdeef56569aed5027","tid":1588901,"uid":67816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:45:59.000Z","msg":"929燒chinazi旗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421ba8b611b1fe9a410a7f5de62c4c0f64b19c49","tid":1588901,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T04:49:43.000Z","msg":"全球燒旗嘅話有咩好講<br />\n929<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />101<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa35343f515daf982b97f4d3116de47184b66121","tid":1588901,"uid":1552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc